**6\. Use Cases**

- Payment for AI/robotic services
- Participation in DAO governance: community members engage in decision-making
- Token accumulation / staking for future benefits
- Funding education and knowledge initiatives — supporting specific projects

**7\. Roadmap**

| **Phase** | **Description** |
| --- | --- |
| Q3 2025 | Creation of new LarGe token, verification, website launch |
| Q4 2025 | Whitepaper release, social campaign |
| Q1 2026 | Planning platform to support AI/robotization |
| Q2 2026 | Funding first subsidized projects (Education Grants) |
| Q3 2026 | Beta testing of LRG-based platform (AI Tool Hub) |

**8\. Social Mission**

LarGe is more than a token — it’s a movement. Our goal is to change the philosophy of labor:

- People should work not for survival, but for development
- Free time should not be “laziness,” but an opportunity to live by one’s own will

